Uche bụ aha Naijiria sitere n'etiti ndị Igbo, nke nwere ike ịpụta "ebumnuche", "uche", ma ọ bụ "echiche"

Ụdị dị iche iche nwere ike ịgụnye Uchechukwu ma ọ bụ Uchenna (nke pụtara "uche Chineke" ma ọ bụ "ebumnuche Chineke"), Ucheoma, (nke pụtara"uche mara mma"), na Uchendu (nke pụtara ""iche echiche / echiche nke ndụ")
Aha Uche nwere ike ịpụta ihe ndị a:
Uche Blessed (amụrụ n'afọ 1995), onye injinia ngwanrọ Naijiria
